        "text": "## Result\n\n**No stability constants measured in supercritical CO₂ were found in the NIST SRD-46 database.**\n\nThe database contains **79,063** stability-constant measurements, and **100%** of them were recorded in **water (H₂O)** as the solvent. There are no entries for supercritical CO₂ (or any other non-aqueous solvent) in this dataset.",
